    "description": "In this short narrative puzzle adventure, you play as a tester who has to overcome increasingly harder logic puzzles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820350/extras/99b311e341a707be037adce1e294a782.poster.avif?t=1684062099\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820350/extras/99b311e341a707be037adce1e294a782.webm?t=1684062099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820350/extras/99b311e341a707be037adce1e294a782.mp4?t=1684062099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Room by room, your actions will be commented on by a test supervisor. Place different sizes of cubes on the corresponding buttons in first person to solve logic-gate-like riddles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820350/extras/c97628bcbb09e7d68a760b487b754e21.poster.avif?t=1684062099\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820350/extras/c97628bcbb09e7d68a760b487b754e21.webm?t=1684062099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820350/extras/c97628bcbb09e7d68a760b487b754e21.mp4?t=1684062099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Playtime on your first run may be around 15-20 Minutes. In succeeding playthroughs, you can challenge yourself with proceeding through the game as fast as possible and even enjoy the party mode.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820350/extras/a653c2ae86ac9e639957f7d4882c1745.poster.avif?t=1684062099\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820350/extras/a653c2ae86ac9e639957f7d4882c1745.webm?t=1684062099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820350/extras/a653c2ae86ac9e639957f7d4882c1745.mp4?t=1684062099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Convert small cubes to a big cube and the other way around, place the cubes on the correct buttons to figure out the challenges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820350/extras/d2734404887121282b3892539eb337ef.poster.avif?t=1684062099\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820350/extras/d2734404887121282b3892539eb337ef.webm?t=1684062099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820350/extras/d2734404887121282b3892539eb337ef.mp4?t=1684062099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Have fun!",
